The paper deals with distributed computing and coded computing, which are both subfields of distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses minimizing waste and optimizing task allocation, which are topics in information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper proposes new task allocation schemes, which falls under the category of computational complexity (cs.CC) and numerical analysis (cs.NA).
